Lifecycle in Class Components
Phase	Method
Mounting	componentDidMount()
Updating	componentDidUpdate()
Unmounting	componentWillUnmount()

Example:

class App extends React.Component {
  componentDidMount() {
    console.log("Mounted");
  }

  componentDidUpdate() {
    console.log("Updated");
  }

  componentWillUnmount() {
    console.log("Unmounted");
  }
}
